WEBVTT

00:03:29.614 --> 00:03:33.907
I saw somebody walking toward me
and he was a German soldier.

00:03:34.380 --> 00:03:38.467
Not only a German soldier --
he was wearing a black uniform.

00:03:38.491 --> 00:03:43.501
That was the uniform of the SS
and they were the most frightening of all.

00:03:44.101 --> 00:03:47.133
And as we came close to each other,

00:03:47.157 --> 00:03:50.612
he beckoned me and picked me up,

00:03:50.636 --> 00:03:55.137
and I remember being terrified
that he would see inside my sweater --

00:03:55.161 --> 00:03:57.065
that he was picking up a little Jew.

00:03:57.089 --> 00:04:00.764
He picked me up
and he hugged me very tight,